The,Helioviewer,Screenshot,API,gives,users,the,ability,to,create,custom,screenshots,of,image,data,from,the,Helioviewer,project,The,Helioviewer,project,consists,of,over,one,million,images,of,the,Sun,spanning,the,past,years,Screenshots,can,be,compiled,into,videos,and,can,include,marker,pins,text,labels,region,polygons,and,scale,indicators,Up,to,three,images,layers,can,be,used,to,generate,videos,Default,response,is,a,JSON,object